stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> PlanReady
  PlanReady --> ExecutionStarting: Run planned states
  ExecutionStarting --> FixtureRunning: adapter ready
  FixtureRunning --> PartiallyComplete: fixture result
  PartiallyComplete --> FixtureRunning: next fixture
  FixtureRunning --> CompletedAllPassing: final result / all passed
  FixtureRunning --> CompletedWithFailures: final result / any failure
  PartiallyComplete --> CompletedAllPassing: final result / all passed
  PartiallyComplete --> CompletedWithFailures: final result / any failure
  ExecutionStarting --> Cancelled: abort or replacement
  FixtureRunning --> Cancelled: abort or replacement
  PartiallyComplete --> Cancelled: abort or replacement
  ExecutionStarting --> InfrastructureFailure: orchestration failure
  FixtureRunning --> InfrastructureFailure: orchestration failure
  CompletedAllPassing --> ExecutionStarting: Run again
  CompletedWithFailures --> ExecutionStarting: Run again
  Cancelled --> ExecutionStarting: Run again
